column4: NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "A02EF8624528C525981764859124E925", "It\'s too hot! I can\'t take it anymore!")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "065EEB2B473E9DFF4CA3F3AFA5F6B317", "I got weird because of the heat.")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "DE85A3B7409B840DA2B4B69812F53CA4", "I know it\'s hot, but... be cool man!")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "0157A9B3417D04E7248F69B2F78790F7", "The more we dig, the hotter it gets. The tunnel is in a volcano.")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "1D00963C4AC0600AFEE783A62BA21BA7", "I don\'t think it\'s the only reason. Maybe there\'s a fire nearby.")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "4C309DE74857C2FD39E5C296D1FD98E4", "I don\'t got a choice. I must bear this heat and keep on digging.")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "D0B7CDE141088827675BBE86984498F0", "We\'ll check out the cause. It\'d be great if the tunnel goes thru.")
NSLOCTEXT("[301194154F646F4C3B552F951CE17690]", "AF25949848A484F8CF85F28CFD7F4BBE", "You are a nice guy. I\'ll hurry and dig this tunnel!")
